title: Royal WS44 Manual
description:
OMG try setting the time without the manual is impossible, the same with any other function.  Oh Boy who thought this was a good idea?  Nice cheap clock thermometer but not exactly intuitive.

In a nutshell to change the time hold the mode button until the time flashes and then the buttons functions indicated at the top start working like time plus and minus and Fahrenheit and Celsius.
When all else fails "read the manual" LOL
